    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing its original, deep-gloss factory paint without a single swirl mark or blemish. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather remains supple and fragrant, free of any wear, creasing, or sun damage. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014the engine bay is spotless, and the service history is documented to the letter. This is more than just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for someone who demands perfection in every stitch and bolt.",
      "price": 44900.0,
