    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in incredible shape\u2014looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following the service schedule. It drives like a dream and the interior still has that new car smell. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm ready for someone else to enjoy this pristine ride. Shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
