      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically superlative example featuring a high-revving, naturally aspirated power plant with a forged rotating assembly and a perfectly indexed valvetrain. This vehicle utilizes a short-throw transaxle with a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring instantaneous torque vectoring and precise power delivery. The chassis maintains factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by a multi-link suspension system with monotube dampers tuned for optimal compression and rebound. Braking performance is anchored by multi-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, showing zero thermal glazing. Every fluid gallery has been flushed with high-performance synthetics, and the ECU logs confirm a history free of over-rev events or ignition retardation. This is a turn-key, concours-ready machine for the discerning driver.",
